snippet.description:

The indoor play area features many types of slides, and large climbing structures. It is divided into three different themes:

- Winter land
- Djungle land
- Underwater world

Indoor playground fun for family and kids.

snippet.description:

We love the slides of course and to run around and climb all over the place. All in all a good indoor playland. This was right before closing time, so not many other kids were playing at the same time. We like it when it feels like we're the only kids there playing. :)

Indoor playground fun for family and kids.
